# UI Rules

## Component Responsibility

- One component = one visual/interaction concern
- Max ~150 lines per component file (split if larger)
- No business logic inside components — call application layer functions
- No domain model mutation inside components — use Zustand actions
- Props shape must be explicitly typed (never use `any`)

## Server vs Client Components

```typescript
// ✅ Default: Server Component (no directive needed)
// Use for: layouts, static content, data fetching shells

// ✅ Client Component: add directive explicitly
'use client';
// Use for: useState, useEffect, event handlers, browser APIs, Zustand

// 📌 Check before adding 'use client':
// Can this be split so only the interactive part is client?
```

## Tailwind CSS Rules

```typescript
// ✅ Use Tailwind utilities
<div className="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 p-6">

// ✅ Complex class combinations → use cn() helper
import { cn } from '@/shared/lib/cn';
<div className={cn('base-class', isActive && 'active-class', className)}>

// ❌ Inline styles (only exception: dynamic values not possible in Tailwind)
<div style={{ color: 'red' }}>

// ❌ CSS modules, styled-components (not in this project)
```

## Component File Structure

```typescript
// 1. Imports (external → internal → types)
// 2. Types / Props interface
// 3. Constants (messages, config values for this component)
// 4. Sub-components (if small and colocated)
// 5. Main component (named export)

export interface StepCardProps {
  step: Step;
  isActive: boolean;
  onDrillDown: (stepId: string) => void;
}

// Group UI strings for future i18n migration
const messages = {
  drillDownLabel: '더 자세히',
  backLabel: '이전 단계',
} as const;

export function StepCard({ step, isActive, onDrillDown }: StepCardProps) {
  // ...
}
```

## Event Handlers

```typescript
// ✅ Named handlers with 'handle' prefix
function handleStepSelect(stepId: string) {
  onDrillDown(stepId);
}

// ❌ Anonymous inline handlers with business logic
<button onClick={() => { setState(...); recalculate(...); }}>
```

## 3D Components (React Three Fiber) — 확정 패턴

> ⚠️ R3F는 반드시 아래 패턴만 사용한다. `'use client'`만으로는 SSR 충돌이 발생한다.

```typescript
// ✅ Step 1: 사용하는 쪽 (page.tsx 또는 상위 Client Component)
// → dynamic + ssr: false 로 import
import dynamic from 'next/dynamic';

const CoffeeViewer = dynamic(
  () => import('@/features/coffee/ui/CoffeeViewer').then(m => m.CoffeeViewer),
  {
    ssr: false,                                    // 서버 실행 완전 차단
    loading: () => <CoffeeViewerSkeleton />,       // 로딩 fallback 필수
  }
);

// ✅ Step 2: CoffeeViewer 파일 자체에는 'use client' 유지
// src/features/coffee/ui/CoffeeViewer/index.tsx
'use client';
import { Canvas } from '@react-three/fiber';
import { OrbitControls, useGLTF } from '@react-three/drei';

// ✅ Step 3: Camera presets는 as const 타입으로
// src/features/coffee/ui/CoffeeViewer/cameraPresets.ts
export const CAMERA_PRESETS = {
  front: { position: [0, 1, 3] as [number, number, number], target: [0, 0, 0] as [number, number, number] },
  top:   { position: [0, 4, 0] as [number, number, number], target: [0, 0, 0] as [number, number, number] },
  side:  { position: [3, 1, 0] as [number, number, number], target: [0, 0, 0] as [number, number, number] },
  zoom:  { position: [0, 0.5, 1.5] as [number, number, number], target: [0, 0, 0] as [number, number, number] },
} as const;

export type CameraPreset = keyof typeof CAMERA_PRESETS;

// ✅ Step 4: GLTF 모델 (준비 전 placeholder, 준비 후 교체)
// 개발 초기 placeholder:
export function DripperModel() {
  return (
    <mesh position={[0, 0, 0]}>
      <cylinderGeometry args={[0.3, 0.5, 0.8, 32]} />
      <meshStandardMaterial color="#c8a882" />
    </mesh>
  );
}

// 모델 준비 후 교체:
